Document Text: Angela Merkel declined Trump's invitation to the G-7 citing a lack of precautionary procedures to prevent Covid-19 infection, a lack of agenda, lack of advance communications, etc. Now Trump announces a draw down in US troops in Germany without a stated reason. Retaliation?
